commit c6b66e76a8cf50aec83b8270b6651755064b56ec
Author: sam
Date:   Wed Nov 12 01:48:58 2003 +0000

      * libee/graphics.c:
        + Renamed ee_color() to ee_set_color(), wrote ee_get_color().
